This code uses the nRF SDK 16, which can be downloaded from
the Nordic Semiconductor site. You will also need a reasonably
recent version of the GCC cross-compiler for ARM, which can be
downloaded from developer.arm.com.

Edit the file "local.config" to reflect where these tools are
installed on your machine. The "nrfjprog" tool must be installed
in your shell path. Finally, the nRF SDK


